SUMMARY:Piano Lunaire at The nanoSTAGE with Cheryl Duvall
DESCRIPTION:Pianist Cheryl Duvall makes her debut at The nanoSTAGE on the Full WORM “BLOOD” MOON. \nCheryll Duvall and Adam Sherkin take the stage in two contrasting sets that features Anna Höstman’s extended\, lyrical and haunting “Harbour.” Adam Sherkin performs Harry Somers’ Second Piano Sonata\, alongside Alison Yun-Fei Jiang’S world premiere\, “Sutra II\,” a Piano Lunaire commission. \nImmerse yourself in a synthesis of the new and dazzling music of our time\, delivered by musicians of intense virtuosic abilities and candid expressive prowess\, ever on display. From 7 to 8pm\, under every full moon this Fall\, meet us at 1001 R Bloor Street West (down the south laneway to the scarlet building double white doors.) \nA Toronto homecoming: PIANO LUNAIRE returns to its west end Toronto origins\, re-inaugurating The nanoSTAGE (now at a new location) on every full moon. On Tuesday\, March 3rd\, join Cheryl Duvall and Adam Sherkin on piano with music music by Anna Höstman\, Harry Somers and Alison Yun-Fei Jiang.. \nPROGRAMME: \nHarry Somers: Sonata No. 2 for piano (1946) \nAlison Yun-Fei Jiang: Sutra II for solo piano (nanoSONATA to Somers’ Sonata No. 2\, 2025) \nAnna Höstman: Harbour (2015) \nSeating is limited to 40 so please purchase tickets in advance as is possible. They are at the 2026 Season price of: $30 \n🐛 🌕\nA few more details: \n\nNo dress code in effect\nBegins promptly at 7pm; end promptly at 8pm\nComplimentary bar (beer\, wine and cider)\nTwo sets (22 mins each) with a 10 min intermission\nAll seats are the same price at $30. If you are able\, please donate to Piano Lunaire Inc. as this series is entirely for-profit and not funded by any public sources to-date\nNote that 10 seats will be available at the door so do attend if you see online sale as “SOLD OUT”\n\nDOORS: 6:30 PMFIRST SET: 7 PMBREAK: 7:25 – 7:35 PMSECOND SET: 7:35PMEND: 8:00 PM \nPlease call: (+1) 416-825-2744 or email: info@pianolunaire.org \nWORM MOON at The nanoSTAGEThe nanoSTAGE1001 R Bloor Street W\, Toronto\, ON M6H 1M1Pianists Cheryl Duvall and Adam Sherkin \n. . . and follow us on Follow us on Instagram: @pianolunaire
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/piano-lunaire-at-the-nanostage-with-cheryl-duvall/
LOCATION:1001 R Bloor Street West\, 1001 R Bloor St W\, Toronto\, ON M6H 1M1\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M6H 1M1
CATEGORIES:Live Music,Performing Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/piano-lunaire-at-the-nanostage-with-cheryl-duvall.png
END:VEVENT
