SUMMARY:Dodie at Danforth Music Hall
DESCRIPTION:Join Dodie’s 2026 tour\, featuring their empowering latest release\, at Danforth Music Hall Theatre on\,Tuesday 3rd March 2026! Beloved for its uplifting anthems and bold messages\, this release has had streams in the millions and dominates playlists worldwide. With sold-out shows like their recent multi-stop frenzy\, Dodie brings new age vibes to Toronto’s progressive heart. This spring March 2026 concert will invite self-expression and inclusivity\, resonating with Ontario’s forward-thinking community. Fans will sing along to tracks that celebrate individuality\, touched by the album’s demanding call to be truly you.
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/dodie-at-danforth-music-hall/
LOCATION:The Danforth Music Hall\, The Danforth Music Hall\, 147 Danforth Ave.\, M4K 1N2 Toronto\, Ontario\, Canada\, Toronto\, M4K 1N2
CATEGORIES:Live Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/dodie-at-danforth-music-hall.jpg
END:VEVENT
